-- Genworth Financial profit rises 25 pct
-- 
-- Tue Jul 29, 2014 05:26PM EDT
-- None



July 29 (Reuters) - Life and mortgage insurer Genworth Financial Inc <GNW.N> posted a 25 percent rise in second-quarter profit as a recovery in the housing market helped its U.S. mortgage insurance business.

Net income rose to $176 million, or 35 cents per share, from $141 million, or 28 cents per share, a year earlier.